list.comment: New Innerjoin builder. Works with multiple tables. Pre work done for work with DTO classes.

task.summary:
Added Mysql Database Connector with dbHandler setup
DAO factory added

Removed some dependency's and added pom.xml from release version.
Main achitecture setup for rebuild. For now with dummy objects and data
Implemented Config file and improved the abstract Databasehandler

Hand made custom data mapper for data resultsets to pojo's. Dbhanders selects made generic.
Added a few pojo's
Output in JSON

Added support for multiple records in custom mapper. Return ArrayList<T>
Also build prepared for filter options
Added support for filter options such as <> operators. Hashmap<String, String> converted to Hashmap<String, List<String>>
Clean operator solution with enum. Added suppress warnings improved filter
Added enums for oder filter And added comments
Completed order by function in filter system

Made Custom Annotations Build an Reflection Layer that reads the Pojo's annotations Build a Join Builder that build a INNER JOIN String.
Combining this with the database layer it creates a dynamically made query. The only that has to be added is the Pojo to be queried
Deleted IRecordMapper. Not needed.
Added new pojo files. Complete db architecture in code
Added Where Alias mapping. Ambiguous reference fix in sql when field in multiple tables
Junction table fix in JoinBuilder. It will now search in other classes for further inner join sections
Build Dynamic SelectBuilder for query execution. Also buildin check for groupby fields
Added option to add groupby clause in query. Find field and table alias based on field string Group Concat field also added by using find field method., To field a field based on a field string
New Innerjoin builder. Works with multiple tables. Pre work done for work with DTO classes.
